  "prompt": "How can I get the mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University?",
  "response": "To obtain your mark-sheet transcripts from Jadavpur University, you can follow these general steps:\n\n1. **Visit the Official Website**: Go to the official website of Jadavpur University. Look for the section related to students or academic services.\n\n2. **Contact the Examination Office**: The examination office is typically responsible for handling transcripts and mark-sheets. Look for their contact information, which might include phone numbers or email addresses.\n\n3. **Application Form**: Check if there\u2019s an online application form for requesting transcripts. Some universities provide an online facility for students to apply for their mark-sheets and transcripts.\n\n4. **Required Documents**: Gather necessary documents that you might need to submit with your application. This can include:\n   - A copy of your previous mark-sheets.\n   - A filled application form.\n   - Identification proof.\n   - Payment receipt for any applicable fees.\n\n5. **Payment of Fees**: Be prepared to pay a fee for the issuance of your transcripts. Details about fees and payment methods should be available on the university's website.\n\n6. **Submit Your Request**: If applying online, submit the request through the university's portal. If you need to go in person, visit the relevant office on campus and submit your application.\n\n7. **Follow Up**: After submitting your application, you may want to follow up to ensure that your request is being processed.\n\n8. **Collecting Your Transcript**: Once your application is processed, you may either receive the transcripts by post, or you might have to collect them in person from the university.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, please consult Jadavpur University's official website or directly contact their examination office.",
